🧠 "Psychological safety is the foundation of innovation!"  
👉 Tip: Encourage a safe environment where team members feel comfortable sharing ideas, giving feedback, and taking risks without fear.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
